### ============================================================
###  badwallet-api (8080) + payment-service (8081) - tests
###  Ordre conseille : 1) seed wallets  2) seed factures auto au demarrage
### ============================================================

### 1. Injecter les portefeuilles de demo (feature/wallet-seeder)
POST http://localhost:8080/wallets/seed

### 2. Creer un portefeuille (feature/wallet-creation)
POST http://localhost:8080/wallets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "771112233",
  "email": "salam@ism.sn",
  "initialBalance": 25000,
  "currency": "XOF"
}

### 3. Lister les portefeuilles (feature/wallet-listing)
GET http://localhost:8080/wallets

### 4. Consulter un portefeuille (feature/wallet-consultation)
GET http://localhost:8080/wallets/770000001

### 5. Consulter le solde
GET http://localhost:8080/wallets/770000001/balance

### 6. Depot (feature/transaction-deposit)
POST http://localhost:8080/deposit/770000003
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 10000,
  "paymentMethod": "WAVE"
}

### 7. Retrait (feature/transaction-withdraw)
POST http://localhost:8080/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "770000001",
  "amount": 5000
}

### 8. Transfert (feature/transaction-transfer)
POST http://localhost:8080/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderPhone": "770000002",
  "receiverPhone": "770000001",
  "amount": 7000
}

### 9. Paiement direct d'un service (feature/payment-services)
POST http://localhost:8080/pay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "770000002",
  "serviceName": "CANAL+",
  "amount": 15000
}

### 10. Consulter les factures via proxy (feature/proxy-factures)
GET http://localhost:8080/external/factures/current?phone=770000001

### 11. Filtrer par service
GET http://localhost:8080/external/factures/current?phone=770000001&unite=SENELEC

### 12. Payer des factures (wallet -> payment-service)
POST http://localhost:8080/pay-factures
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "770000001",
  "serviceName": "SENELEC",
  "factureReferences": ["FAC-SEN-001", "FAC-SDE-001"]
}

### 13. Historique des transactions (feature/transaction-history)
GET http://localhost:8080/wallets/770000001/transactions

### ============================================================
###  Appels directs au payment-service (8081)
### ============================================================

### Factures du mois courant
GET http://localhost:8081/factures/current?walletCode=WAL-DEMO0001

### Factures par references
GET http://localhost:8081/factures?references=FAC-SEN-001&references=FAC-SDE-001

### Factures sur une periode
GET http://localhost:8081/factures/periode?walletCode=WAL-DEMO0001&start=2026-01-01&end=2026-12-31
